high_descs: Walk to the microwave on your right.
Grab a cup from the microwave.
Go to the kitchen counter on your left.
Place the cup on the counter.
Grab a knife from the counter.
Put the knife in the cup.
anns.task_desc: Take a cup and put a knife in it.

high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink, then hang a right and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and take the white cup out of the microwave, then close the door.
Turn left to face the counter.
Put the white cup on the counter to the right of the spatula.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Put the butter knife into the white cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a butter knife in a white cup on the counter.

high_descs: Walk to the sink then turn right and go to the microwave
Take the cup out of the microwave
Turn left to face the kitchen counter
Put the cup on the counter
Pick up the knife from behind the cup
Put the knife in the cup
anns.task_desc: Put a knife into a cup
